  mit-krb5-1.4.3-r3.ebuild, mit-krb5-1.5.1.ebuild:
  s/einfo/elog/
  Removed static USE wrt bug #155530 (thx vapier)
  Security cleanup wrt bug #143240
  Acknowledged by exg

